title: Unknown packing error

embed.description: Imgur: The magic of the Internet

body:
I installed the game like a couple of months ago and uninstalled it but I'm trying to install it again and this is happening.
I get this unknown packing error every time I launch the installer. please help, I'm running in administrator.

replies.body: Ah snap, those dll's can run into some errors here and there if something blocks or deletes them due to thinking they are some type of virus. I don't want things to go wrong, so be sure to hit up our techs in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so they can walk you through some steps to get this fixed up as quickly and smoothly as possible.

Are you trying to run an old installer than you had previously downloaded months ago, or running it from a freshly downloaded installer? If you're trying to do a fresh install, double check to make sure all old files were deleted from when you previously uninstalled.
I am installing from the latest installer and all old files have been removed.
